articles.author: Victor Goury-Laffont
articles.title: Dutch prime minister to skip COP29 after Amsterdam football violence - POLITICO Europe
articles.description: PM Dick Schoof says “major social impact” of last week’s clashes will keep him from climate summit in Azerbaijan.
articles.content: "I will not be going to Azerbaijan next week for the U.N. Climate Conference COP29. Due to the major social impact of the events of last Thursday night in Amsterdam, I will remain in the Netherlands,… [+1603 chars]
